description: The first thing you notice right off the bat is that there is a significant size different between Kaleb and Sean, but that didn’t stop Kaleb from doing what he wanted to do. When we asked him what he was looking forward to doing to Sean, he answered “I just wanna make him feel good.” Even though Sean was the bottom, his aggressive and dominant personality shined through, but Kaleb did exactly what he set out to do…make Sean feel good!
title: Kaleb & Sean: Bareback
